that is the error you get when you dont have a public ssh key connected to your cloud  init config file in proxmox.
first you are going to need 2 ssh keys. (Pub key) and (pri key)
After generating the keys all you have to do is add the (pub key) in the cloud init config.
if it still giving the same error. go to ((solved)(2-2)WARNING REMOTE HOST IDENTIFICATION HAS CHANGED!) for the next fix. ( ˶°ㅁ°) !!